        "body": "<p>If, as said in a comment, data is of type <code>Stream&lt;Object&gt;<\/code>, this code should do the job:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>JavaRDD parsedData = data.map( o -&gt; o.toString() )\n    .map( s -&gt; \n    {\n        String[] sarray = s.split( \" \" );\n        double[] values = new double [sarray.length];\n        for( int i = 0; i &lt; sarray.length; i++ ) \n        {\n            values[i] = Double.parseDouble( sarray[i] );\n        }\n        return Vectors.dense( values );\n    });\n    parsedData.cache();\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
